6. Block the source IP if confirmed malicious
', '["https://www.elastic.co/guide/en/elasticsearch/reference/current/modules-scripting-painless.html","https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1059/"]', 'exists("log.message") &&
(
  (contains("log.message", "script") && (
    contains("log.message", "Runtime.getRuntime") ||
    contains("log.message", "ProcessBuilder") ||
    contains("log.message", "exec(") ||
    contains("log.message", "getRuntime().exec") ||
