6. Block the source IP if confirmed malicious
', '["https://owasp.org/www-community/attacks/Path_Traversal","https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1083/"]', 'exists("origin.ip") &&
exists("origin.path") &&
(
  contains("origin.path", "../") ||
