Next Steps:
1. Verify if the role creation/modification was authorized
2. Identify the user who performed the operation
3. Review the granted privileges and assess risk
4. Check for other unauthorized role changes
5. Remove unauthorized roles or privileges immediately
6. Implement role-based access control with least privilege
', '["https://www.postgresql.org/docs/current/sql-createrole.html","https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1098/"]', 'exists("log.msg") &&
(
  regexMatch("log.msg", "(?i)CREATE\\s+ROLE\\s+\\w+.*SUPERUSER") ||
  regexMatch("log.msg", "(?i)ALTER\\s+ROLE\\s+\\w+.*SUPERUSER") ||
