7. Implement additional application-level security controls if needed
8. Check for any bypass attempts or evasion techniques being used
', '["https://docs.fortinet.com/document/fortiweb/7.6.0/administration-guide/981691/syntax-based-sql-xss-injection-detection","https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1190/"]', 'equals("action", "deny") && 
