6. Deploy rate limiting for GraphQL endpoints
', '["https://cheatsheetseries.owasp.org/cheatsheets/GraphQL_Cheat_Sheet.html","https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1190/"]', 'exists("origin.ip") &&
(
