5. Review connection patterns for beaconing behavior
6. If suspicious, terminate the connection and scan the host
', '["https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1571/","https://www.cisco.com/en/US/technologies/tk648/tk362/technologies_white_paper09186a00800a3db9.html"]', 'exists("origin.ip") &&
