3. Review authentication logs for failed/successful logins from the source IP
4. Examine process execution logs on both source and target systems
5. Validate if the detected services (SMB, RDP, WMI) are authorized for this source
6. Check for privilege escalation attempts on target systems
7. Review network segmentation to ensure proper access controls
8. Correlate with endpoint detection tools for additional IOCs
', '["https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1021/","https://attack.mitre.org/tactics/TA0008/","https://www.snort.org/rule_docs/"]', '(contains("log.alert.signature", ["lateral movement", "psexec", "wmi", "rdp brute", "smb scan"]) ||
