2. Check web server logs for corresponding exploitation attempts (SSRF, XXE, JNDI)
3. Determine if this is authorized penetration testing activity
4. If unauthorized, investigate the target application for vulnerabilities
5. Block the OOB interaction domains at the DNS resolver
6. Check for successful exploitation indicators on the target systems
7. Review WAF/IDS logs for correlated attack signatures
