2. Verify if the file access was authorized
3. Review network traffic for large data transfers
4. Check datastore browser access logs
5. Restrict datastore access permissions
6. Implement file integrity monitoring on datastores
', '["https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1005/"]', 'exists("log.message") &&
(
  (contains("log.message", ".vmdk") && (
    contains("log.message", "download") ||
    contains("log.message", "GET /folder/") ||
    contains("log.message", "scp") ||
