', '["https://attack.mitre.org/techniques/T1574/002/","https://www.mandiant.com/resources/blog/dll-side-loading-a-thorn-in-the-side-of-the-anti-virus-industry","https://hijacklibs.net/"]', '(equals("log.eventCode", "4688") || equals("log.winlogEventId", 4688)) &&
